we have come to a decision.

38:37.181 --> 38:38.580
Mr. Scott...

38:43.154 --> 38:46.612
<i>And it's a long way down</i>

38:48.559 --> 38:51.084
Haley, I'm sorry, okay?
I'm sorry for the way this looks,

38:51.162 --> 38:54.131
but before you say anything,
just know that it's my fault.

