Daddy's home!

39:14.952 --> 39:17.477
Hey, buddy. What's up?

39:18.956 --> 39:20.514
Mommy and I need to
talk right now, okay?

39:20.591 --> 39:22.718
So why don't you go out back
and shoot a round?

39:22.793 --> 39:24.420
