Try to make five free throws in a row

39:24.495 --> 39:26.759
and I'll be out there in a sec, okay?

39:28.999 --> 39:32.025
<i>And it's a long way down</i>

39:32.136 --> 39:34.434
It's a simple question, Nathan.

39:35.573 --> 39:37.336
Did you kiss her?

39:38.342 --> 39:39.366
No.

39:42.847 --> 39:45.042
But she kissed me.

39:47.084 --> 39:50.110
HALEY: You looked me right in the eye
and you said that there's nothing else.

39:50.187 --> 39:52.280
You said, "There's nothing more."

39:52.356 --> 39:53.618
And I have been through
a lot with you, Nathan.

39:53.691 --> 39:55.659
I've been through better and worse,
and sickness and health,

39:55.726 --> 39:57.216
but I will not do infidelity.

39:57.294 --> 39:59.819
It wasn't like that, okay? I wasn't into her.

39:59.897 --> 40:02.422
You call kissing Carrie and watching her
swim naked not being into her?

40:02.500 --> 40:04.968
I didn't kiss her. How many times
do I have to tell you that?

40:05.035 --> 40:06.093
NATHAN: It wasn't me.

40:06.170 --> 40:09.196
- NATHAN: It was Carrie. Don't you see?
- No, it's you. It's always you.

40:09.273 --> 40:10.934
When are you gonna learn?
When are you gonna stop

40:11.008 --> 40:13.408
making bad choices that threaten
everything that we've built?

40:13.477 --> 40:16.139
Everything I've ever done
was for this family, Haley.

40:16.213 --> 40:18.841
Well, excuse us for being
such a weight around your neck.

40:18.916 --> 40:20.816
I didn't say that, okay?
And you know I didn't mean that.

40:20.885 --> 40:21.874
Don't put words in my mouth.

40:21.952 --> 40:24.420
HALEY: Well, somebody needs to,
because you have a really nasty habit

40:24.488 --> 40:26.422
